Advantages
1. Trees are very easy to explain
2. Decision trees more closely mirror human decision-making than other regression and classification approach
3. XGTrees can be displayed graphically, and are easily interpreted even by a non-expert
4. Trees can easily handle qualitive predictors without the need to create dummy vatiables


Disadvantages
1. Trees generally do not have the same level of predictive accuracy as some of the other and regreddion and classification approaches